 * Pure-logic where possible (parser is testable without DB) — search/timeline
 * touch DB but are read-only and use $wpdb->prepare everywhere (no raw SQL).
 *
 * Public helpers:
 *   dinoco_sn_parse_search_query( $q ) : array
 *     → Parse "DNCSS* sku:X status:registered phone:0812345678" into struct.
 *
 *   dinoco_sn_search_plates( $parsed, $limit = 50 ) : array
 *     → Execute SQL with prepared statements; return rows joined w/ pool_meta.
 *
 *   dinoco_sn_get_timeline_for_sn( $sn, $limit = 50 ) : array
 *     → Audit events for an S/N + actor display name resolution.
 *
 *   dinoco_sn_mask_phone_for_display( $phone ) : string
